| **frontend-specialist** | UX Audit | `python ~/.claude/skills/frontend-design/scripts/ux_audit.py .` |
| **frontend-specialist** | A11y Check | `python ~/.claude/skills/frontend-design/scripts/accessibility_checker.py .` |
